<ul>
<li><strong>Data Type :&nbsp;</strong>All elements have same NumPy data typ=
e.</li>
<li><strong>Item Size :</strong> Memory size of each item in bytes</li>
<li><strong>Shape :</strong> Dimensions of the array</li>
<li><strong>Data :</strong>&nbsp;The easiest way to access the data is trou=
gh indexing , not this pointer.</li>
